des:
Ask for Kashmir Facts, and learn about what has happened with the beautiful land of Kashmir.

To start, just say "Alexa, launch Kashmir Facts" or "Alexa, open Kashmir Facts" to get a fact".

At anytime, you can stop by saying "Alexa, stop"
